addr: 1000 North Alameda Street Los Angeles, CA 90012
title: Los Angeles Women's HIV/ AIDS Task Force Annual Treatment Summit and Leadership Awards   "Be the Best You!"
desc: The Los Angeles Women's HIV/ AIDS Task Force is proud to host its 8th annual Treatment Summit and Leadership Awards. We welcome all those who stand in solidarity to promoting the mission and vision of our Organization and alike are dedicated to raising awareness to the continued need to support the needs of women and girls living with and affected by HIV/ AIDS in Los Angeles County. This event aims to provide a space for the sharing of information and resources.
